scripts.comment: 操作员组简介 Intro to Operators group

一只蝙蝠随机飞进来，如果它碰到了狗，它就会说“抓到你” - 蝙蝠和狗的位置都将被重置 - 蝙蝠不能在人行道上飞翔 - 狗只能在马路和人行道上行走 a bat fly in random and if it touches the dog, then it says "catcha" - position of both bat and dog will be reset - bat cannot fly beyond the road - dog can only walk on road and pavement
